      • getDistance

        public float getDistance()
        Returns:
        returns the route distance. Method loops through coordinate list. If list is empty, return 0.0f. Sets current location by calling getLatitude() and getLongitude() methods. On each loop, increment i and set currentLoc to coordinates held in position i of coordinates list. Do same for nextLoc but add 1 so it retrieves the coordinates of the position in front of current location. Using distanceBetween() it calculates distance between the two locations and add results to distance variable.
